      <title>瑞士央行再次降息以刺激经济并推动瑞郎上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/snb-cuts-rate-again-to-aid-economy-and-stem-gains-in-the-franc</link>
